{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/EmuKit/emukit/issues/210","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/EmuKit/emukit","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/EmuKit/emukit/issues/210/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/EmuKit/emukit/issues/210/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/EmuKit/emukit/issues/210/events","html_url":"https://github.com/EmuKit/emukit/issues/210","id":448556365,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU0NDg1NTYzNjU=","number":210,"title":"Fixed sample of representer points for entropy search used throughout whole optimization","user":{"login":"henrymoss","id":32096840,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjMyMDk2ODQw","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/32096840?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss","html_url":"https://github.com/henrymoss","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":7,"created_at":"2019-05-26T11:19:12Z","updated_at":"2019-07-24T15:31:34Z","closed_at":"2019-07-24T15:31:34Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"Hi \r\n\r\nThe provided examples of entropy search and the multi-fidelity entropy search acquisitions currently only sample a single set of representer points, which they then use for the whole optimization.\r\n\r\nThis set should ideally be re-sampled at the beginning of each BO step (after updating the GP and proposal function), adaptively responding to our observations and focusing computational resources on promising areas.\r\n\r\nUsing the same set throughout requires a much larger choice of sample size to cover the search space and allow high-precision optimization.\r\n\r\nMy current workaround is to add a step that does this resampling at the end of each BO step.\r\n```\r\n\r\ndef resampler(loop,loop_state):\r\n    loop.candidate_point_calculator.acquisition.update_parameters()\r\nloop.iteration_end_event.append(resampler)\r\n```\r\n\r\nI think this should be made clearer in the documentation or added automatically within the OuterLoop utility.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"henrymoss","id":32096840,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjMyMDk2ODQw","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/32096840?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss","html_url":"https://github.com/henrymoss","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/henrymoss/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/EmuKit/emukit/issues/210/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/EmuKit/emukit/issues/210/timeline","performed_via_github_app":n